stockwhip
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a whip used in moving stock [esp.on cattle stations where stock are unused to being driven or managed.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
